data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. ***PRICE REDUCED*** Opportunity alert - Priced under market value!!  Welcome home to this amazing 4 bedroom, 3 bath pool home, nestled in the rolling hills of Clermont.  As you enter the home, designed for family living & entertaining, you will notice this floor-plan features a spacious entryway, formal living and dining rooms, a bright kitchen that opens to the family room, and the 3-way split bedroom plan which gives this home efficiency and flexibility.  The primary bedroom is a true oasis, featuring a large walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with a relaxing tub, a separate shower, and double sinks. The three additional bedrooms are spacious and comfortable and have easy access to the remaining bathrooms. Outside, the home's private pool is the perfect place to relax and enjoy the warm Florida sun.  The screened-in lanai provides plenty of space for outdoor dining and entertaining, while the pool deck offers plenty of space for lounging in the sun.  Located just minutes away from historic Downtown Clermont, shopping, dining, chains of lakes, Walt Disney World and much more!  ***NEW ROOF and SCREEN ENCLOSURE COMPLETED AUG 2023***
